| **PUBLIC Schema** | Dropped (not used) |

### Tags Applied

Each database will be tagged with:

| Tag | Value |
|-----|-------|
| `DOMAIN` | {{ data_product_domain | upper }} |
| `ENVIRONMENT` | {{ data_product_environment | upper }} |
| `DATAPRODUCT` | {{ data_product_name | upper }} |
| `ZONE` | (varies per database) |

**Note:** Tags capture all components regardless of whether they appear in the database name. This ensures consistent cost allocation across all account strategies.

### Ownership

| Stage | Owner | Notes |
|-------|-------|-------|
| **Initial** | SYSADMIN | Creates the database |
| **After Role & Access Control** | Data Product Owner | Receives ownership for delegated administration |

Ownership transfer occurs in the Role & Access Control task after the data product owner role is created.